<article-title xml:lang="en"><![CDATA[WHY DOES "BRAZILIAN FASHION" WANT TO BE GLOBAL? INEQUALITIES IN INTERNATIONAL SYMBOLIC EXCHANGES AND THE ETHOS OF THE AGENTS OF NATIONAL FASHION]]></article-title>
